{"calories":"600","carbs":null,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"It’s no secret that we love a good culinary mashup. Inspired by one of her favorite sandwiches, the Vietnamese bánh mì, Chef Elana deconstructed the dish into a hearty, seasonal rice bowl. Cauliflower and sweet potato are roasted in a caramelized soy and Sriracha glaze, then piled high atop jasmine rice. The bowl is garnished with the traditional bánh mì fixins: pickled vegetables, spicy mayo, and plenty of fragrant cilantro. Get ready to be bowled over (see what we did there?)!","difficulty":"medium","external_id":"656087ca92","fat":null,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17919/2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0098_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17919/hero_2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0098_1.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17919/menu_small_2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0098_1.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17919/small_square_2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0098_1.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17919/medium_square_2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0098_1.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17919/recipe_profile_page_2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0098_1.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17921/2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0098_2.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17923/2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0107_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17923/menu_small_2025_Cauliflower_Bahn_Mi_Bowls___0107_1.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Cauliflower Bánh Mì Bowls with Sriracha Mayo","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"35-45","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":null,"public_slug":"cauliflower-bahn-mi-bowls-with-sriracha-mayo","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/10205/recipe_card20170116-4-1340ch.pdf","recipe_id":2025,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Cauliflower Bánh Mì Bowls","subtitle":"with Sriracha Mayo","title":"Cauliflower Bánh Mì Bowls","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did!\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBe sure to evenly space the vegetables apart on the baking sheet so they roast in the oven instead of steam.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["2 6\" small pots, 1 with lid","aluminum foil","baking sheet"],"id":2025,"ingredients":["jasmine rice","dark soy sauce","Sriracha","dark brown sugar","cauliflower","sweet potato","English cucumber","red radishes","cilantro","rice wine vinegar","shredded carrots","mayonnaise"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"jasmine rice","quantity":"0.75","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/138/medium_square_RICE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"dark soy sauce","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1111/medium_square_soy_sauce_dark_1.jpg"},{"name":"Sriracha","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/440/medium_square_SRIRACHA_copy.jpg"},{"name":"dark brown sugar","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/108/medium_square_brown-sugar-dk2.jpg"},{"name":"cauliflower","quantity":"12.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/319/medium_square_cauliflower-test.jpg"},{"name":"sweet potato","quantity":"9.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1272/medium_square_medium_square_sweet-potato-2.jpg"},{"name":"English cucumber","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/462/medium_square_cucumber.jpg"},{"name":"red radishes","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1081/medium_square_medium_square_medium_square_veg-radish-temp.jpg"},{"name":"cilantro","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1305/medium_square_medium_square_cilantro-test.jpg"},{"name":"rice wine vinegar","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/197/medium_square_RICE_WINE_VINEGAR_2_copy.jpg"},{"name":"shredded carrots","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/378/medium_square_shredded-carrots.jpg"},{"name":"mayonnaise","quantity":"1.5","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1261/medium_square_medium_square_mayonnaise.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["canola oil","water","kosher salt"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"canola oil","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png"},{"name":"water","quantity":"1.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Cook Rice","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16517/recipe_card_size_1._Cook_Rice.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. In a small pot, combine \u003cstrong\u003erice\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e1.25 cups water\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eand bring to a boil over high heat. Reduce heat to medium low, cover, and simmer until water is fully evaporated, 10-12 minutes. Remove pot from heat and let stand, still covered, for 10 minutes. Fluff rice with a fork, then cover to keep warm until ready to serve.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16522/recipe_card_size_2._Prepare_Ingredients_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile rice cooks, in a large bowl, whisk together \u003cstrong\u003esoy sauce\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e1 packet Sriracha\u003c/strong\u003e (or skip if you don't want heat), \u003cstrong\u003eall but 1 teaspoon brown sugar\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003e2 teaspoons canola oil\u003c/strong\u003e. Rinse all produce. Cut \u003cstrong\u003ecauliflower\u003c/strong\u003e into .5-inch pieces and cut \u003cstrong\u003esweet\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003epotato\u003c/strong\u003e into .5-inch dice, then add both to bowl with sauce mixture and toss to coat. Quarter \u003cstrong\u003ecucumber\u003c/strong\u003e lengthwise and thinly slice crosswise. Thinly slice \u003cstrong\u003eradishes\u003c/strong\u003e. Pick \u003cstrong\u003ecilantro\u003c/strong\u003e leaves, discarding stems.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast Cauliflower and Sweet Potato","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16525/recipe_card_size_3._Roast_Vegetables_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePour \u003cstrong\u003ecauliflower\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003esweet potato\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eany remaining sauce\u003c/strong\u003e onto a foil-lined baking sheet. Arrange in a single layer and roast until tender and caramelized, about 20 minutes (see Recipe Tip).\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Pickle Vegetables","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16528/recipe_card_size_4._Pickle_Vegetables_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile vegetables roast, in a separate small pot, heat \u003cstrong\u003erice\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ewine\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003evinegar\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining brown sugar\u003c/strong\u003e over medium heat. Cook, stirring, until sugar is dissolved, 2-3 minutes. Remove pot from heat. Add \u003cstrong\u003ecarrots\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ecucumber\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eradishes \u003c/strong\u003eto pot with pickling liquid and stir to combine. Set aside to pickle until ready to serve. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make Sriracha Mayo","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16530/recipe_card_size_5._Make_Sriracha_Mayo.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eIn a small bowl, stir together \u003cstrong\u003emayonnaise\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining packet Sriracha \u003c/strong\u003eto combine (use half or less for milder heat). Set aside for serving. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate Bánh Mì Bowls","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16533/recipe_card_size_6._Plate_Dish.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eDrain \u003cstrong\u003epickled\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003evegetables\u003c/strong\u003e. Divide \u003cstrong\u003erice\u003c/strong\u003e between serving bowls and top with \u003cstrong\u003eroasted vegetables\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003epickled\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003evegetables\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003ecilantro\u003c/strong\u003e. Drizzle over \u003cstrong\u003eSriracha mayo\u003c/strong\u003e and dig in!\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Spicy","slug":"spicy","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Soy","slug":"soy","hex_color":""},{"name":"Egg","slug":"egg","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Loose Grain","slug":"loose-grain","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Spicy","slug":"spicy","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}